WEBVTT

00:00:29.667 --> 00:00:31.476
noutro positivo

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.351
ao permitirmos que do noso descontento

00:00:34.375 --> 00:00:36.042
naza o cambio.

00:00:37.417 --> 00:00:40.601
O 6 de xaneiro do 1999,

00:00:40.625 --> 00:00:42.393
eu estaba traballando en Londres

00:00:42.417 --> 00:00:44.851
cando comezaron a informar nas noticias

00:00:44.875 --> 00:00:48.143
da invasión rebelde na miña cidade natal,

00:00:48.167 --> 00:00:50.208
Freetown, Serra Leoa.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:53.893
Miles de persoas perderon a vida,

00:00:53.917 --> 00:00:57.351
e os corpos cubriron as rúas de Freetown.

00:00:57.375 --> 00:01:01.434
A tía maior do meu home foi queimada viva,